snippet: Duffy Waldorf shot a five-under-par 67 to take a one-stroke lead after the second round of the Champions Tour’s Principal Charity Classic in Des Moines.
abstract: Duffy Waldorf takes second-round lead at Champions Tour’s Principal Charity Classic in Des Moines; other golf news noted.
